    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入这场末世FPS僵尸大战，与64名玩家组队对抗僵尸群，拯救人类！背叛队友，撕裂团队。升级解锁新武器、福利和服装等！带上你最喜欢的装备，加入战斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/8b07aad96727351cf4154021e26b61b6.poster.avif?t=1765578316\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/8b07aad96727351cf4154021e26b61b6.webm?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/8b07aad96727351cf4154021e26b61b6.mp4?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特技</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想怎么玩，就怎么玩解锁特技，按你的方式战斗。游戏支持使用50多种特技进行攻击、防御，或帮助其 他猎人。你还可以为僵尸角色选择特技，扔出更多的肢体部件、降低伤害值，或减缓猎人的速度，让其 他僵尸也能咬上一口！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/d48b2372ac89c7508ce74d0ac6cae23d.poster.avif?t=1765578316\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/d48b2372ac89c7508ce74d0ac6cae23d.webm?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/d48b2372ac89c7508ce74d0ac6cae23d.mp4?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义猎人角色！在游戏中解锁新服装，来炫耀你的装备吧。最棒的是，僵尸角色被暴击时，也可以使 用相同的服装！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/4b859e67f1364db6114f0a24270b72dc.poster.avif?t=1765578316\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/4b859e67f1364db6114f0a24270b72dc.webm?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/4b859e67f1364db6114f0a24270b72dc.mp4?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重复可玩性</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《乌鸦部落》的每一个回合都采用了不同的地图，精心制作的画面，为玩家呈现绝佳的游戏体验。地图 还支持预设不同的天气状况，因此，即使是同一张地图，每次游戏的视觉体验也完全不一样。多达64名 玩家的混战现场，每一轮游戏都有不一样的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/aeb33954c732c40a39ae19b414354e00.poster.avif?t=1765578316\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/aeb33954c732c40a39ae19b414354e00.webm?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179490/extras/aeb33954c732c40a39ae19b414354e00.mp4?t=1765578316\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >死而复生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中通过杀戮和帮助队友，获得更多的积分，决胜排行榜。如果场上所有猎人都被杀死，得分最高 的玩家将再次复活，制造混乱</p>",
